
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-tsitkov-audit-00.txt'>
    <title>"Audit in OAuth 2.0", Zhanna Tsitkov</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-tsitkov-audit-00.txt</link>
    <description>This specification is an effort to provide guidelines for implementing the Audit functionality for OAuth 2.0 enabled environments.  The data of interest for the OAuth 2.0 audit includes permissions, scopes, policies and other authorization and authentication related information.  It can be used by user agents and authorization services for fast violation response, credential revocation, or by government agencies and various institutions for forensic analysis.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-10-14T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
